2011-05-09T06:12:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/hsin-kuang-steel-april-sales-fall-47-92-table-2031-tt.html
HSIN KUANG STEEL said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 47.92% to NT$513,648,000 from NT$986,309,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            513,648          986,309    
YOY%             -47.92%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,557,610        2,987,410   
YOY%             -14.39% 
=================================================================
 